#: src-en/data/events_sector_laststand.xml.append:30
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_laststand.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"TRUE_LAST_STAND_START\"]/mod:findLike/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"On the vidscreen appears several Federation and Engi officers, as well as "
"Admiral Tully in the center. \"Is that a RadiKal ship? SOLDIERS, MAN THE- "
"... Wait what do you mean you're Federation? Oh. Dear heavens, Is that how "
"low we have to go? Even if we defeat the Rebellion, this might be enough to "
"fuel a new one. Honestly, I'm glad you made it all the way here, but in the "
"name of all things sacred you better make sure all the atrocities you funded"
" or committed yourself were worth it, by defeating the Flagship.\""

